platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Now heres how you build a sequel! With The Room Three, Fireproof Games kept everything we love about this seriesits chilling atmosphere, mind-bending puzzles, and beautiful visualswhile making masterful enhancements. Its no wonder its an Honorable Mention for Best Mobile Game at this years Game Developers Conference. The story continues with trials set by a creepy new nemesis, The Craftsman. As you explore huge areas and tiny ones, the challenges feel increasingly epic, and a better-than-ever hint system ensures that finding solutions is super-rewarding.
